---
const diagnosticItems = [
  { label: 'Claridad', detail: 'Oferta entendible en segundos', tone: 'text-primary' },
  { label: 'Conversión', detail: 'Narrativa, objeciones y CTA', tone: 'text-secondary' },
  { label: 'Velocidad', detail: 'Carga rápida para campañas', tone: 'text-green-400' },
  { label: 'Mobile-first', detail: 'Pensada para tráfico real', tone: 'text-blue-400' },
];
---

<section id="hero" class="relative flex min-h-[92vh] flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden bg-background-dark pt-28 pb-20 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-28">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#4f4f4f24_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#4f4f4f24_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:18px_28px] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_70%_45%_at_50%_0%,#000_65%,transparent_100%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-[520px] w-[520px] rounded-full bg-primary/20 blur-[140px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 h-[520px] w-[520px] rounded-full bg-secondary/10 blur-[150px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-14 lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="lb-hero-content lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-3 border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-4 py-2">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(226,255,0,0.8)]"></span>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-primary">Para negocios digitales con tráfico y oferta validada</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-display text-4xl font-black leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl">
          No necesitás otra web linda. Necesitás una landing que convierta tráfico en
          <span class="relative inline-block text-black">
            <span class="relative z-10 px-2">oportunidades reales.</span>
            <span class="absolute inset-0 -rotate-1 bg-primary"></span>
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-7 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-zinc-300 sm:text-lg">
          Diseño, copy y desarrollo landing pages de alto rendimiento para coaches, consultores, marcas personales, ecommerce y negocios digitales que quieren convertir más visitas en consultas, leads o ventas.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
          <a
            href="#apply"
            class="group inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center border-2 border-primary bg-primary px-7 py-4 text-base font-black text-black shadow-brutal-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-brutal sm:w-auto"
          >
            Solicitar diagnóstico
            <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
          </a>
          <p class="max-w-xs text-sm leading-6 text-text-dim">
            Respuesta en menos de 24h. Sin compromiso. Proyectos desde USD 1,000.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden border border-border-dark bg-surface-dark/80 p-4 shadow-2xl">
          <div class="absolute -right-24 -top-24 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-primary/20 blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="mb-5 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-border-dark pb-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/70"></span>
              <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/70"></span>
              <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/70"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-text-dim">Landing audit panel</span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            {diagnosticItems.map((item, index) => (
              <div class="group border border-border-dark bg-background-dark p-4 transition-all hover:border-primary/40">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                  <div>
                    <p class={`font-display text-lg font-bold ${item.tone}`}>{item.label}</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-400">{item.detail}</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">0{index + 1}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <div class="mt-5 border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 p-4">
            <p class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white">El objetivo no es decorar.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-400">Es construir una página que explique, genere confianza y empuje la acción correcta sin fricción.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
